reviewText: 5 more episodes that cover a range of years. All were filmed in the 40's or some of Bill Boyd's later films. The quality of  the prints is high and so is the quality of the sound. They take me back to my childhood days where they could be seen on the TV but without the luxury of todays technology.  If you like to see a spirit  with the desire to do what is right these are right up your alley!
Title: Hopalong Cassidy, Vol. 6

reviewText: If you love Westerns, GOOD old westerns, you will love the Hopalong Cassidy movies.  Loved the movie, always loved Hopalong.  In this day and these times Hopalong takes us back to a simple, predictable time that is to me fun and enjoyable without stress and just plan relaxing to watch.  These movies are  digitally remastered and wonderful to watch after being made so many years ago, that is amazing to me.  AND what a laugh, Hoppy had the most robust laugh I have ever heard.  These Hopalong movies are certainly worth buying from AMAZON.COM and enjoying from time to time for those who love good Westerns.  The most important thing for me is that whatever I buy at AMAZON.COM, and that means ANYTHING you can possibly think of, if it isn't right I know they will  make it right for me and that shopping with AMAZON.COM online is the only way to go.
